ly calibrated [V/Fe] from ASPCAP  <li> cr_fe real NOT NULL,          -- empirically calibrated [Cr/Fe] from ASPCAP  <li> mn_fe real NOT NULL,          -- empirically calibrated [Mn/Fe] from ASPCAP  <li> fe_h real NOT NULL,           -- empirically calibrated [Fe/H] from ASPCAP  <li> co_fe real NOT NULL,          -- empirically calibrated [Co/Fe] from ASPCAP  <li> ni_fe real NOT NULL,          -- empirically calibrated [Ni/Fe] from ASPCAP  <li> cu_fe real NOT NULL,          -- empirically calibrated [Cu/Fe] from ASPCAP  <li> ge_fe real NOT NULL,          -- empirically calibrated [Ge/Fe] from ASPCAP  <li> rb_fe real NOT NULL,          -- empirically calibrated [Rb/Fe] from ASPCAP  <li> y_fe real NOT NULL,           -- empirically calibrated [Y/Fe] from ASPCAP  <li> nd_fe real NOT NULL,          -- empirically calibrated [Nd/Fe] from ASPCAP  <br> Sample call to get aspcap element abundances:  <br><samp>  <br>select TOP 10 a.apstar_id, b.*  <br> from aspcapStar a CROSS APPLY dbo.fAspcapElems( a.aspcap_id ) b  </samp>  <br>see also fAspcapElemsAll, fAspcapElemErrs, fAspcapElemFlags ','0');
